cs.AI, cs.LO, cs.DB, cs.LG, cs.CR

This paper deals with reasoning and knowledge representation in multi-relational networks, which are common in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and databases (cs.DB). The paper also introduces a new logic and reasoner, which falls under the category of logic in computer science (cs.LO). The use of evidential reasoning and support for partial and contradictory knowledge also suggests a connection to machine learning (cs.LG) and cryptography (cs.CR).
